### ============================================================
### Health & OpenAPI — events-importer (port 8081)
### ============================================================

### Health check (Actuator)
GET {{importer-host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### OpenAPI spec (JSON)
GET {{importer-host}}/v3/api-docs
Accept: application/json

### Swagger UI (open in browser)
GET {{importer-host}}/webjars/swagger-ui/index.html
